Catalyst-Plugin-HTML-Scrubber version 0.01
==========================================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Catalyst
  HTML::Scrubber

